%N A396029 Decimal expansion of the probability that Buffon's needle will land on exactly one line when dropped on a triangular tiling in which the altitude of each triangle equals the length of the needle.
%H A396029 Michael D. Perlman and Michael J. Wichura, <a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/2683484">Sharpening Buffon's Needle</a>, The American Statistician, Vol. 29, No. 4 (1975), pp. 157-163.
