%H A396029 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buffon&#39;s_needle_problem">Buffon's needle problem</a>.
%H A396029 Wikipedia, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Triangular_tiling">Triangular tiling</a>.
%H A396029 <a href="/index/Tra#transcendental">Index entries for transcendental numbers</a>.
%F A396029 Equals 3*(8-sqrt(3))/(4*Pi) - 5/4.
%F A396029 Equals 1/4 - A396028.
%F A396029 Equals 1 - A396028 - A102519 - (A240935 - 1/4).
